---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SAVOY | Esperienza Sensoriale</title>
    
    <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js" is:inline></script>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#050505] text-[#e0e0e0] antialiased selection:bg-white selection:text-black overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 top-0 px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center mix-blend-difference">
        <a href="/" class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-[0.4em] font-light uppercase" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            Savoy
        </a>
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-12 text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            <a href="/camere" class="hover:italic transition-all duration-300">Residenze</a>
            <a href="/spa" class="hover:italic transition-all duration-300">Thermae</a>
            <a href="/ristorante" class="hover:italic transition-all duration-300">Gusto</a>
        </div>
        <a href="#booking" class="text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border-b border-white pb-1 hover:pb-2 transition-all" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            Booking
        </a>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center overflow-hidden">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540541338287-41700207dee6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80" alt="Savoy Dark" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 scale-105" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-[#050505]"></div>
        
        <h1 class="relative z-10 text-[15vw] leading-[0.8] text-center text-white font-light" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
            <i>Oltre</i> <br> IL TEMPO
        </h1>
        <p class="relative z-10 mt-12 text-[10px] tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-gray-400" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            Bibione, Venezia
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20">
        
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="sticky top-32 h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611892440504-42a792e24d32?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Dettaglio Architettura" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-1000">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center pt-20 md:pt-0">
            <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                La Nuova <br> <i>Dimensione</i>.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-12 text-sm md:text-base font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-md" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>
                    Dimentica tutto ciò che sai sull'ospitalità alberghiera. Abbiamo svuotato gli spazi, tolto il superfluo e lasciato solo l'essenziale: luce, materia, silenzio.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Un monolite di design sospeso tra la sabbia di Bibione e le acque termali. Un luogo progettato non per dormire, ma per fuggire dal mondo reale.
                </p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/camere" class="text-white text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Esplora le Stanze <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative h-[80vh] w-full flex items-center my-32">
        <div class="absolute inset-0">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80" alt="Ristorante" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20">
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10 w-full text-center px-4">
            <h2 class="text-[10vw] text-white font-light leading-none" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Gusto</i> BRUTALE.
            </h2>
            <a href="/ristorante" class="mt-8 inline-block text-white text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                Scopri il Menù
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 border-t border-white/10 text-center">
        <p class="text-[#555] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            © 2026 Savoy Beach Hotel. Architettura & Design.
        </p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>